              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Virtua Fighter will be available on Steam for the first time ever thanks to the new Virtua Fighter 5 REVO edition launching January 27. Fans can snag a discounted preorder for the Steam version at Fanatical, where the<a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dpbolvw.net%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fvirtua-fighter-5-revo&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fvirtua-fighter-5-revo-pc-preorders-are-30-off%2F1100-6528706%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f%26utm_source%3Ddlvr.it%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow"> standard version is down to just $14</a> (was $20), and the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dpbolvw.net%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fgame%2Fvirtua-fighter-5-revo-30-th-anniversary-edition&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fvirtua-fighter-5-revo-pc-preorders-are-30-off%2F1100-6528706%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f%26utm_source%3Ddlvr.it%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">30th Anniversary edition that comes with tons of extra content</a> is on sale for $35 (was $50).</p><p>Preordering either version will get you three character customization items based on vintage Sega consoles like the Genesis, Saturn, and Dreamcast, that you can use to add some flair to your favorite fighter.</p><div title="[Various] Virtua Fighter 5 REVO Preorders" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3045" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="[Various] Virtua Fighter 5 REVO Preorders" data-collection="">                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.dpbolvw.net\/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https:\/\/www.fanatical.com\/en\/game\/virtua-fighter-5-revo&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo">Virtua Fighter 5 R.E.V.O. for Steam</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.dpbolvw.net\/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https:\/\/www.fanatical.com\/en\/game\/virtua-fighter-5-revo&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo">$14 (was $20)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>Virtua Fighter 5 REVO will support rollback netcode for online matches. This has become the preferred way to play fighting games online as it enables smoother battles worldwide, and its inclusion in Virtua Fighter 5 REVO put it on par with the netcode in other modern fighting games like Street Fighter 6. The game also supports a 4K resolution, updated textures, and numerous balance changes to the 19-character roster. Like a Dragon developer, Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio has also added new modes, including16-player online tournaments and leagues.</p>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo-30-th-anniversary-edition" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.dpbolvw.net\/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https:\/\/www.fanatical.com\/en\/game\/virtua-fighter-5-revo-30-th-anniversary-edition&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo-30-th-anniversary-edition">Virtua Fighter 5 R.E.V.O. - 30th Anniversary Edition</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo-30-th-anniversary-edition" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.dpbolvw.net\/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https:\/\/www.fanatical.com\/en\/game\/virtua-fighter-5-revo-30-th-anniversary-edition&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.dpbolvw.net/click-100770772-13797872?sid=subid_value&amp;url=https://www.fanatical.com/en/game/virtua-fighter-5-revo-30-th-anniversary-edition">$35 (was $50)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>The 30th Anniversary version of Virtua Fighter 5 REVO comes with a lot of DLC. This package gets you 30th Anniversary-themed costumes for all characters, all Virtua Fighter titles original soundtracks and unreleased music, archival artwork, exclusive in-game rank titles, the Yakuza series Collaboration Pack DLC, and the Virtua Fighter Legendary Pack DLC. </p>                      </div>   </div><p><em>Disclosure: GameSpot and Fanatical are both owned by Fandom.</em></p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/grab-3-movies-on-4k-blu-ray-for-only-33-at-amazon-while-you-can/1100-6528683/">Grab 3 Movies On 4K Blu-Ray For Only $33 At Amazon While You Can</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/final-fantasy-7-remake-physical-edition-gets-ps5-reprint-snag-it-while-you-can/1100-6528630/">Final Fantasy 7 Remake Physical Edition Gets PS5 Reprint - Snag It While You Can</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-2500-piece-legend-of-zelda-lego-set-is-now-available-at-amazon/1100-6523747/">The 2,500-Piece Legend Of Zelda Lego Set Is Now Available At Amazon</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/mario-kart-lego-sets-are-available-now-check-out-all-six-in-the-launch-lineup/1100-6528603/">Mario Kart Lego Sets Are Available Now - Check Out All Six In The Launch Lineup</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/fortnite-lego-sets-launch-at-major-retailers-including-amazon-and-walmart/1100-6528629/">Fortnite Lego Sets Launch At Major Retailers, Including Amazon And Walmart</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/backbone-one-iphone-and-android-controller-is-50-off/1100-6524903/">Backbone One iPhone And Android Controller Is 50% Off</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-lord-of-the-rings-the-war-of-the-rohirrim-4k-blu-ray-limited-edition-steelbook-preorders/1100-6528224/">The Lord Of The Rings: The War Of The Rohirrim 4K Blu-Ray Steelbook Up For Preorder At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/metaphor-refantazios-massive-official-strategy-guide-up-for-preorder-at-amazon/1100-6528507/">Metaphor: ReFantazio Is Getting A Nearly 600-Page Official Strategy Guide</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
