            <title><![CDATA[Five Nights At Freddy’s: Into The Pit And Help Wanted 2 Are Getting Physical Editions Later This Year]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/five-nights-at-freddys-into-the-pit-and-help-wanted-2-are-getting-physical-editions-later-this-year/1100-6528746/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/five-nights-at-freddy%E2%80%99s-into-the-pit-and-help-wanted-2-are-getting-physical-editions-later-this-year.1079670/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/five-nights-at-freddys-into-the-pit-and-help-wanted-2-are-getting-physical-editions-later-this-year/1100-6528746/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div id="site-main">

      
                    
  
